                    <p>All hosts and guests must verify their identity with government-issued ID and phone number before booking or listing.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="col-md-4">
                <div class="feature-card">
                    <div class="feature-icon">
                        <i class="fas fa-lock"></i>
                    </div>
                    <h3>Secure Payments</h3>
                    <p>All transactions are processed through our secure platform. Never pay or communicate outside of HomeAway.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="col-md-4">
                <div class="feature-card">
                    <div class="feature-icon">
                        <i class="fas fa-headset"></i>
                    </div>
                    <h3>24/7 Support</h3>
                    <p>Our global safety team is available around the clock to assist with any issues or concerns.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<!-- Safety Tips -->
<section class="safety-tips">
    <div class="container">
        <h2 class="section-title">Safety Tips for Everyone</h2>
        
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-lg-6">
                <h3><i class="fas fa-home text-primary me-2"></i> For Hosts</h3>
                
                <div class="tip-card">
                    <h4>Secure Your Property</h4>
                    <p>Install quality locks, security cameras in common areas, and consider a safe for valuables.</p>
                </div>
                
                <div class="tip-card">
                    <h4>Screen Guests Carefully</h4>
                    <p>Review profiles, read reviews, and communicate through HomeAway's messaging system before accepting bookings.</p>
                </div>
                
                <div class="tip-card">
                    <h4>Set Clear House Rules</h4>
                    <p>Clearly outline expectations regarding guests, noise levels, and property use in your listing.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="col-lg-6">
                <h3><i class="fas fa-user text-primary me-2"></i> For Guests</h3>
                
                <div class="tip-card">
                    <h4>Research Listings Thoroughly</h4>
                    <p>Read reviews carefully, verify the location on maps, and look for properties with multiple positive reviews.</p>
                </div>
                
                <div class="tip-card">
                    <h4>Communicate Through HomeAway</h4>
                    <p>Keep all communication and payments on the platform to ensure you're protected by our policies.</p>
                </div>
                
                <div class="tip-card">
                    <h4>Check Safety Features</h4>
                    <p>Look for listings that mention smoke detectors, first aid kits, and emergency contact information.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<!-- Emergency Section -->
<section class="emergency-section">
    <div class="container">
